'''Houkese''' was the language of the [[Houk/Legends|Houks]]. It was the official language of the Houk native [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Lijuter]], but not of their colony on the [[Weequay/Legends|Weequay]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] [[Sriluur/Legends|Sriluur]]. It was mainly formed by grunts, with subtle tonal inflections to differentiate words that would otherwise sound the same. [[Houkese alphabet|Written Houkese]] used primitive ideograms with one letter to represent each simple verbs, but complex pictograms to represent nouns.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

''Chikra'' was a Houk term of endearment for young.

